<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.9.9">
<l>yāṉē yeṉṉai yaṟiyaki lātē</l>
<l>yāṉē yeṉṟaṉa tēyeṉ ṟiruntēṉ</l>
<l>yāṉē nīyeṉ ṉuṭaimaiyu nīyē</l>
<l>vāṉē yēttumem vāṉava rēṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, I could not know myself.</l>
<l>Thinking “I am mine only” I was.</l>
<l>I am you, and my possession is you alone,</l>
<l>o our bull of the celestials who is praised in heaven.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
